  "title": "Junior Accounts Executive",
  "description": "<p>- Preparation for full set of accounts</p><p>- Preparation of accounting schedules</p><p>- Assist on client yearly audit and tax</p><p>- Preparation of payroll, CPF/IR8A form for clients</p><p>- Preparation of GST reports and submission to IRAS</p><p>- Computation of local taxes, submission of tax filing and compliance with local tax regulations</p><p>- Preparation of unaudited financial statements</p><p>- Other duties and responsibilities as assigned by manager</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>- Degree in Accountancy/ACCA</p><p>- Possess CA/CPA will have added advantageous</p><p>- 1-3 years of relevant experience</p><p>- Strong analytical and problem-solving skills</p><p>- Ex auditors are welcome</p>",
